(1, 1725117923, 'Your Guide to the Free Winter Update', '2020-11-17', '  It\'s here! Well, almost. The Animal Crossing: New Horizon\'s Winter Update will be available on November 19! Here\'s what we know:\r\n\r\nTurkey Day (November 26)\r\nTurkey Day\r\nLooks like everyone can celebrate American Thanksgiving this year in Animal Crossing!', '            <h3 style=\"\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">It\'s here! Well, almost. The Animal Crossing: New Horizon\'s Winter Update will be available on&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">November 19!&nbsp;</span>Here\'s what we know:</p></h3><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Turkey Day (November 26)</h3><h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"Turkey Day\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/51gbzj2xzCH9l0jMexEowJ/b9519a6b6f780f9d6547e400a2db2a9b/Screen_Shot_2020-11-17_at_10.02.46_AM.png\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Looks like everyone can celebrate American Thanksgiving this year in Animal Crossing! Meet&nbsp;<i>first-class chef&nbsp;</i><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><i>Franklin</i></span>! He will ask you to gather some ingredients to create a feast in the plaza. A reason to&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">keep those pumpkin patches</span>&nbsp;for just a while longer!!</p></h3><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Toy Day (December 24)</h3><h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"Toy Day\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/3iOdILG6rkNwgwkDuN3lPk/4ddd42f9775981d1fc6e3568698ab0e7/Screen_Shot_2020-11-17_at_10.03.11_AM.png\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">To celebrate Christmas, Animal Crossing is holding an event on Christmas Eve (December 24).</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Jingle the black-nosed reindeer will be coming to your island to ask for help with delivering presents to your residents!</p></h3><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">New Nook Miles Redemptions</h3><h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"Nook Miles Redemptions\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/7r43ym5XtiH7yTygS05xhK/514818dce68394a0491b3ed2b2b21128/Screen_Shot_2020-11-17_at_10.03.37_AM.png\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\"></p></h3><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Top 6 Stylish Hairstyles</h3><h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"Hairstyles\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/2ZbGeWUkf3rxkH1rzgHPpr/7e69ac38a33447ab46344e7f1f726152/Screen_Shot_2020-11-17_at_10.04.03_AM.png\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Taneisha Bracken&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/nintendo-create-more-inclusive-hairstyles-for-animal-crossing-acnh?utm_content=cl_sharecopy_23059769_en-US%3A0&amp;recruiter=980571661&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=tap_basic_share&amp;utm_term=f9ae35d3bb1c4cf183df2e5b410a8018\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(242, 190, 126);\">petitioned</a>&nbsp;to make Animal Crossing hairstyles more inclusive to all races, and this update is a step in the right direction!</p></h3><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Hip Reaction Collection</h3><h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"Reactions\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/6OWx1EVgSfoTWXtZD6qsB8/a7a95535fb423174d8432439e6d0261a/Screen_Shot_2020-11-17_at_10.08.08_AM.png\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">There are&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">9 new reactions</span>&nbsp;available for redemption at the Nook Stop! They include:</p><ul style=\"list-style: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\"><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;üòä Sit down</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üëã&nbsp;Wave goodbye</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">ü§≥ Take a picture</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üëÉ Sniff sniff</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üí™ Work out</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üßò&nbsp;Yoga</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">ü§ó&nbsp;Here you go</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">ü§© Excited</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">ü§™ Ta-da</p></li></ul></h3><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Most Anticipated? HOUSE STORAGE UPGRADE!</h3><h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"Storage Upgrade\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/6rIJgLDHfA2P5yaZU5p98O/74516b2e2ae4034089f3bc9f4bfbe111/Screen_Shot_2020-11-17_at_10.04.31_AM.png\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YDFl5lFPTr4\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(242, 190, 126);\">official video</a>&nbsp;released by Nintendo hints that you will have to dish out Bells out for it, but it is still VERY exciting that there is a house storage upgrade!!! This makes me think Custom Design Slots might soon be expandable as well...</p></h3><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Save Data Transfer</h3><h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"Transfer Save Data\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/4GpnU6PBdlirghQadEuwDr/5925a521cb3ca957d3dad9fcee5b15b9/Screen_Shot_2020-11-17_at_10.49.15_AM.png\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">You will now&nbsp;<i>officially</i>&nbsp;be able to transfer your saved data to a new Switch as of November 19th! Some lucky souls were able to contact Nintendo and do so more recently, but the option was supposed to only be if your old Switch was stolen on broken!</p></h3>'),
(3, 1725127094, 'Your Guide to the Spooky Update!', '2020-10-01', ' Grow pumpkins! üéÉ\r\nWatering pumpkins\r\nYou can obtain pumpkin starters from Lief (for 140 Bells) or Nook\'s (280 Bells). The starters take 3 days to grow, and yield 1-3 pumpkins depending on if you water them or not. (Water them the day you plant them, as well as the following day to ensure you will get 3 pumpkins per plant!)\r\n\r\nPumpkin Patch\r\nThere are 4 types of pumpkins:\r\n\r\nüéÉ Orange (used to craf', ' <h3 style=\"\">Grow pumpkins! üéÉ</h3><p><img alt=\"Watering pumpkins\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/a0uqIg1dnCXNuAK5KyFPw/d527d7ad8c766a3f87bd765f5db60643/EjQuzQ8VkAAz3RP.jpeg\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">You can obtain&nbsp;pumpkin starters&nbsp;from Lief (for&nbsp;140 Bells) or Nook\'s (280 Bells). The starters take 3 days to grow, and yield&nbsp;1-3 pumpkins&nbsp;depending on if you water them or not. (Water them the day you plant them, as well as the following day to ensure you will get 3 pumpkins per plant!)</p><p><img alt=\"Pumpkin Patch\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/7s0iJtiFM8ILwwT1H1BoXo/8a9052a9a9d047a45c2d1b39d52ca6b6/EjQuzRCUcAEdvbd.jpeg\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">There are&nbsp;4 types&nbsp;of pumpkins:</p><ul style=\"list-style: none;\"><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Orange (used to&nbsp;craft&nbsp;items)</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Yellow*</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ White*</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Green*</p></li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">* used to&nbsp;customize&nbsp;items (in place of Customization Kits)</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">It\'s important to note that pumpkins are very similar to flowers‚Äî when you pick them, they grow again and again! So&nbsp;don\'t&nbsp;be like me and&nbsp;buy 50 pumpkin starters&nbsp;thinking you\'ll need to constantly replant them!</p><h3 style=\"\">Dress up!</h3><p><img alt=\"Eye/Skin Colour\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/2YFktDpIEeA7bDALiPJJ6v/04e98a6febac517d717c9ec0e2e7f8c7/EjQu68sUcAArMBX.jpeg\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">New&nbsp;body-paint and eye-colour&nbsp;variations became available with this update! Simply&nbsp;redeem Nook Miles&nbsp;for \"Body-Paint Costume Tips\" and \"Exploring New Eye Colors\" at the Nook Stop!</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">As for clothing‚Äî there are new Halloween themed clothing items available at Ables every day! Also be sure to check in with Kicks in the plaza, as he will have some items as well.</p><h3 style=\"\">Get \"Spooky\" Items!</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Check in with your villagers and pop balloons daily throughout October to get \"Spooky\" recipes!</p><p><img alt=\"Spooky DIYs\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/458upg5yDDEVqIb4wjyGxi/b6d468f20f84252bfb8c609229c9e197/EjQu69JVcAEAp9u.jpeg\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Spooky Recipes include:</p><ul style=\"list-style: none;\"><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Spooky Arch</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Spooky Candy Set</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Spooky Carriage (get from Jack on Oct 31st)</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Spooky Chair</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Spooky Fence</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Spooky Garland</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Spooky Lantern</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Spooky Lantern Set</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Spooky Scarecrow</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Spooky Standing Lamp</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Spooky Table</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Spooky Table Setting</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Spooky Tower</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üéÉ Spooky Wand</p></li></ul><p><img alt=\"Gifted pumpkins\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/1mZbDuph3B9Rq0RwHoMcRe/9ef8e815ce9be6109f4c11d6f72fbf62/EjQuzQ3U8AA0AyM.jpeg\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Fun fact: If a villager is crafting a Spooky item and you already have that recipe, they will gift you candy or pumpkins instead!</p><p><img alt=\"Spooky Items at Nook\'s\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/7FPmVKVcxlKlu3Mbd5o7wC/85543a1cf86ed04a68f2cbe0ef248418/EjQu68lVgAAgrN_.jpeg\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Buyer Beware: Nook\'s will try to sell you already crafted DIY items for $$$!&nbsp;If you wait it out, you will probably get that specific DIY within a day or two. Or, if Bells aren\'t really an issue for you, splurge to get those Halloween items faster!!!</p><h3 style=\"\">Collect candy!</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">You will want to collect candy to&nbsp;trick or treat&nbsp;with on Halloween night! In return, your villagers will gift you other spooky items, or lollipops to give to Jack.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">You can only buy&nbsp;one piece of candy&nbsp;per day at Nook\'s Cranny! It\'s definitely not something you\'ll want to forget about!</p><p><img alt=\"Candy at Nook\'s\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/1phBak9H450fYSY6LLx7Ac/ec86bec9062cd42ee4f53cea0082c6bf/EjQuzRDU4AA8AL2.jpeg\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none;\"><br></p>'),
(4, 1725127911, 'How to Maximize Your Acorn & Pinecone Return This Fall...', '2020-09-11', 'It\'s been over a week since Fall began in Animal Crossing: New Horizons for players in the Northern Hemisphere, but it seems people are still struggling when it comes to getting Tree\'s Bounty crafting materials (acorns from hardwood trees and pinecones from cedar trees). Here\'s how to maximize your return of acorns and pinecones in only a few minutes!\r\n\r\nStep 1: Shake trees in open spaces!\r\nTree s', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">It\'s been over a week since Fall began in Animal Crossing: New Horizons for players in the Northern Hemisphere, but it seems people are still struggling when it comes to getting Tree\'s Bounty crafting materials (acorns from hardwood trees and pinecones from cedar trees). Here\'s how to&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">maximize your return of acorns and pinecones</span>&nbsp;in only a few minutes!</p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Step 1: Shake trees in open spaces!</h3><p><img alt=\"Tree shaking grid\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/578fvVHg8voSkO6FgRYCk7/3f1a7c99cce1a6c6608417a3689e29b1/acorns2.jpg\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Before you start shaking a tree, imagine this grid. There are&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">14 possible places</span>&nbsp;for tree branches, acorns or pinecones to fall. Start on one side of the tree and shake with all your might until 8 spaces are full of items. Then, switch sides to shake out the remaining 6 items. This step should only take a moment or two.</p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Step 2: Collect your materials!</h3><p><img alt=\"Shaken Tree Syndrome\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/4YKxHcDBWQG6a4QgaQGkEz/8702b293b4506a3be441dde9370285c6/acorns4.jpeg\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Sometimes you will get 1 Tree\'s Bounty material, sometimes you\'ll get several. It\'s all the luck of the draw...</p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Step 3: Repeat!</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">There is no specific number of pinecones/acorns per tree, so the beauty of this method is you don\'t need to run around to several trees... You can literally use one hardwood and one cedar tree to collect all of the Fall materials your heart desires!</p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">10 minutes of shaking two trees yielded...</h3><ul style=\"list-style: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\"><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üçÇ 153 tree branches</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üçÇ 11 acorns</p></li><li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">üçÇ 6 pinecones</p></li></ul>'),
(5, 1725135190, 'Adopt your Dreamie: Marshal Giveaway!', '2021-08-21', 'To celebrate reaching 200 followers on my instagram, I\'ve decided to do a Dreamie Giveaway!\r\n\r\nMarshmallow Giveaway!\r\nPrizes:\r\nFirst Prize: Adopt an ungifted Marshal from my island, Unchartia! Second Prize: 10NMT and 2 stacks of star frags.\r\n\r\nTo Enter:\r\n1. Be following me on instagram.\r\n\r\n2. Like the giveaway post!\r\n\r\n3. Post to your story (for an extra entry).\r\n\r\n4. Fill out this form (this is h', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">To celebrate reaching 200 followers on my<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/island.horizons\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(242, 190, 126);\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">instagram</span></a>, I\'ve decided to do a Dreamie Giveaway!</p><p><img alt=\"Marshmallow Giveaway!\" src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/ccpqjwcq0rmr/7ty7LghulYbV2xhmgJEZfp/0386052c66aee27ee5eebe48b23a5e52/marshgiveaway\" style=\"width: 614.688px; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; border-style: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\"></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">Prizes:</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">First Prize:</span>&nbsp;Adopt an ungifted Marshal from my island, Unchartia!&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Second Prize:</span>&nbsp;10NMT and 2 stacks of star frags.</p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);\">To Enter:</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-famil